noticeDescription:
IN THE MATTER OF THE ONTARIO HERITAGE ACT

R.S.O. 1990 CHAPTER 0.18 AND

482 AND 488 WELLINGTON STREET WEST

CITY OF TORONTO, PROVINCE OF ONTARIO

 

NOTICE OF PASSING OF BY-LAW 1124-2022

 

Take notice that the Council of the City of Toronto has passed By-law 1124-2022 to designate 482 and 488 Wellington Street West (Spadina-Fort York, Ward 10) as being of cultural heritage value or interest.
title: Notice of Passing of By-law - 482 and 488 Wellington Street West
